  A^ano turojiEiY EaqoliY faqado A^anaY laki"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Mercy on thee! O Jinneeyeh,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jin~iY~a","text_ar":"جِنِّىَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jin~iy~apu","text_ar":"جِنِّيَّةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"doth it appear fit to thee that thou shouldst restore my reason? for the time hath come for thee"},{"kind":"text","text":"to do so], a woman resembling a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jin~iy~ap","text_ar":"جِنِّيَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is meant, either because of her beauty, or in her changeableness. (TA.)       -A2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tallness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"length and height,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a camel's hump. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n6503","headword_ar":"جَنًى","root":"jnY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janiY~N","text_ar":"جَنِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whatever is gathered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plucked;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janaApN","text_ar":"جَنَاةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whatever is gathered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plucked, from trees,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"&c.;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(so in a copy of the S;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janaApN","text_ar":"جَنَاةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) so that these two words are of the same class as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hiq~N","text_ar":"حِقٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hiq~apN","text_ar":"حِقَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or the latter of them is a n. un.: (TA:) or the former signfies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is gathered from trees while fresh;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janiY~N","text_ar":"جَنِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) or this last is an epithet applied to fruit, signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"just gathered"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plucked;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gathered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plucked, while fresh:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majonFY","text_ar":"مَجْنًى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", also, pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majaAnK","text_ar":"مَجَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fruit gathered"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plucked:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 369:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janFY","text_ar":"جَنًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fruit"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ready to be gathered"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plucked"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; so in the Kur lv. 54: (Jel:) and is applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fresh ripe dates:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grapes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"truffles,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) and even"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cotton:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gold,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) which is collected from its mine: (TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cowries,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) as though gathered from the sea: (TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"honey,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when it is gathered:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajonaA='N","text_ar":"اَجْنَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajonK","text_ar":"اَجْنٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajonuYN","text_ar":"اَجْنُىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) Hence the saying,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"h`*aA janaAY wa xiyaAruhu fiyhi\n                      \n                     \n                        A_i*okul~u jaAnK yaduhu A_ilaY fiyhi"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is what I have gathered, and the best of it is in it; when every gatherer"},{"kind":"text","text":"but myself"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"has his hand to his mouth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: or, accord. to one reading,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wa hijaAnuhu fiyhi","text_ar":"وَ هِجَانُهُ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(which has the same meaning, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hjn","text_ar":"هجن"},{"kind":"text","text":"): a prov., ascribed by Ibn-El-Kelbee to 'Amr Ibn-' Adee El-Lakhmee, the son of the daughter of Jedheemeh: he says that Jedheemeh had ordered the people to gather for him truffles, and some of them ate the best that they found; but ' Amr brought to him the best that he found, and addressed to him these words: and 'Alee is related to have repeated them on an occasion of his entering the government-treasury; meaning that he had not defiled himself with anything of the tribute belonging to the Muslims, but had put it in its places. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","S","TA","Msb","Jel","Fr"]},{"entry_id":"n6505","headword_ar":"جَنِىٌّ","root":"jnY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janFY","text_ar":"جَنًى"},{"kind":"text","text":". Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Dates cut from the tree."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}